1
00:00:52,160 --> 00:00:52,880
Wait.

2
00:00:56,240 --> 00:00:58,120
I brought back what you wanted.

3
00:00:58,480 --> 00:00:59,740
Where is what I wanted?

4
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:02,440
Don't you trust me?

5
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,060
After all, you are Mr. Hei now.

6
00:01:09,320 --> 00:01:11,000
Then let's cancel our deal.

7
00:01:12,039 --> 00:01:14,100
Give me back the principal I gave you.

8
00:01:15,320 --> 00:01:17,120
And we will go our separate ways.

9
00:01:18,160 --> 00:01:18,960
Zhang Qian.

10
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:25,480
Call me Mr. Hei.

11
00:01:26,320 --> 00:01:27,120
Mr. Hei.

12
00:01:28,080 --> 00:01:28,600
Okay.

13
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:30,200
Mr. Hei.

14
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:50,280
Take the money later.

15
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:51,340
Thank you, Mr. Hei.

16
00:01:51,800 --> 00:01:52,960
If there is a next time,

17
00:01:52,960 --> 00:01:54,240
I will definitely take your hand.

18
00:01:54,240 --> 00:01:55,039
Yes.

19
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:10,800
A pinhole camera.

20
00:02:14,720 --> 00:02:16,040
It seems your original plan

21
00:02:16,040 --> 00:02:17,920
was to wait until we were losing badly

22
00:02:17,920 --> 00:02:19,000
to come and save us.

23
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:21,600
You trust me that little?

24
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:26,220
I never thought about saving you.

25
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:31,280
I originally wanted Fat Cat to win the money back himself.

26
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:32,520
But you showed up,

27
00:02:33,440 --> 00:02:36,440
giving me a perfect chance to settle a personal score.

28
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:44,079
My first plan was to wait until you lost all the money

29
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:47,040
and got beaten half to death fighting Brother Hui.

30
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:51,000
Then I would show up with the hidden video of him cheating,

31
00:02:51,079 --> 00:02:53,340
use it as an excuse to shut down his place,

32
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:56,180
vent my anger, and get the money back.

33
00:02:57,440 --> 00:02:59,440
I just didn't expect

34
00:03:00,760 --> 00:03:02,640
you not only won the money back,

35
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:05,840
but also gave me a huge secret.

36
00:03:11,920 --> 00:03:13,050
I heard everything.

37
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:34,720
Hello?

38
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:37,040
198 Xinhua Road.

39
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:53,360
In the past,

40
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,360
I was sorry.

41
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:59,079
Since the truth is out,

42
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:00,880
let the past be the past.

43
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:03,560
The old Zhang Qian should come back too.

44
00:04:06,160 --> 00:04:08,160
It's not that easy to let the past go.

45
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:10,690
Coming back is even harder.

46
00:04:11,920 --> 00:04:14,800
Besides, this isn't over yet.

47
00:04:25,520 --> 00:04:27,380
Be careful of the girl behind you.

48
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:36,320
Drive.

49
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:02,120
I'll go buy some medicine.

50
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:03,320
Wait for me in the car.

51
00:05:07,320 --> 00:05:08,200
What do you need?

52
00:05:08,200 --> 00:05:09,080
Just looking.

53
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:13,560
Sorry.

54
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:14,940
I'm five minutes late.

55
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:20,960
Here is the information you asked for.

56
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:21,760
By the way,

57
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:23,720
when I hacked into the casino's surveillance,

58
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:25,480
I found someone else hacking it too.

59
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,920
I tried to trace their IP,

60
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:28,360
but failed.

61
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:30,080
The other guy is a pro.

62
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:31,970
Better than you?

63
00:05:33,320 --> 00:05:34,320
Much better.

64
00:05:38,159 --> 00:05:40,420
Did you bring what I asked you to prepare?

65
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:46,159
By the way.

66
00:05:47,159 --> 00:05:48,760
Help me look up someone else.

67
00:05:48,960 --> 00:05:50,600
I'll send you the info later.

68
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:52,520
Okay.

69
00:05:58,640 --> 00:05:59,200
Hey, gorgeous.

70
00:05:59,200 --> 00:06:00,040
Thanks for the Wi-Fi.

71
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:02,170
Otherwise, I would have been delayed.

72
00:06:05,960 --> 00:06:06,960
Are you hungry?

73
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:09,700
How about going to my place for some noodles?

74
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,490
Who exactly are you?

75
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:10,720
If I'm not mistaken,

76
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:12,240
this can vibrate.

77
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:14,000
Morse code.

78
00:07:15,320 --> 00:07:16,880
Who sent you?

79
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:20,480
Where is my daughter?

80
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:33,200
You enjoy seeing me played for a fool, don't you?

81
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:34,400
I'm telling you.

82
00:07:34,400 --> 00:07:35,040
For my daughter,

83
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,240
I would do anything.

84
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,700
I'll ask you one last time.

85
00:07:37,760 --> 00:07:41,320
Who sent you?

86
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,840
I don't know.

87
00:07:44,520 --> 00:07:47,600
Someone paid me to do this.

88
00:07:49,200 --> 00:07:51,000
You're not going to tell me, huh?

89
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:30,640
Get lost.

90
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:38,600
Hold on.

91
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:05,380
Did you bring what I asked you to prepare?

92
00:09:38,040 --> 00:09:39,640
When I was a police officer,

93
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:42,080
I had an informant named Bai.

94
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:43,680
Sang Rong killed him.

95
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:44,800
What I want to ask is,

96
00:09:44,800 --> 00:09:47,680
who leaked his identity as an informant?

97
00:09:47,920 --> 00:09:51,200
Actually, we didn't even know he was your informant.

98
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,720
The reason Bai was killed

99
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:56,720
is because he committed a major taboo in the underworld.

100
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:58,180
He slept with Rong's wife.

101
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:59,760
Your boss is Sang Rong.

102
00:10:00,560 --> 00:10:01,760
Want to take revenge?

103
00:10:01,760 --> 00:10:03,880
To be honest, I do have this thought.

104
00:10:03,880 --> 00:10:05,160
And if you think about it,

105
00:10:05,160 --> 00:10:06,520
he's also my brother-in-law.

106
00:10:06,520 --> 00:10:09,040
Since the truth has come to light,

107
00:10:09,040 --> 00:10:10,400
let the past be the past.

108
00:10:12,640 --> 00:10:14,640
It's not that easy to let the past go.

109
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:16,320
This matter is not over yet.

110
00:10:24,040 --> 00:10:24,640
What are you doing?

111
00:10:24,640 --> 00:10:25,200
Heige is not seeing guests.

112
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:26,160
You can't go in here.

113
00:10:26,160 --> 00:10:26,840
I told you.

114
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:30,600
Boss, this...

115
00:10:30,880 --> 00:10:32,200
Leave us for now.

116
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:04,530
I thought you didn't eat cilantro.

117
00:11:05,960 --> 00:11:07,480
I used to not eat cilantro.

118
00:11:08,160 --> 00:11:08,960
Then,

119
00:11:09,640 --> 00:11:10,560
Lao Bai asked me,

120
00:11:10,560 --> 00:11:12,040
"Are you allergic?"

121
00:11:12,040 --> 00:11:12,960
I said no.

122
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:15,000
Lao Bai then told me how good cilantro is.

123
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:17,000
He said it has vitamins,

124
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:18,160
is good for the eyes,

125
00:11:18,160 --> 00:11:19,560
and good for the stomach.

126
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:22,460
He also called me a picky eater and too fussy.

127
00:11:27,040 --> 00:11:28,880
After Lao Bai was gone,

128
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,580
I tried cilantro once.

129
00:11:32,760 --> 00:11:35,360
I found that the more I eat it, the more I like it.

130
00:11:36,160 --> 00:11:36,960
So,

131
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:39,330
one shouldn't be too stubborn.

132
00:11:40,160 --> 00:11:41,200
Sometimes,

133
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:44,720
you have to listen when others make sense.

134
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:48,810
You can't always be trapped in your own thoughts.

135
00:11:49,320 --> 00:11:50,080
Right?

136
00:12:10,280 --> 00:12:12,200
Domestic Type 64.

137
00:12:12,680 --> 00:12:13,600
Seven bullets.

138
00:12:14,560 --> 00:12:16,890
I used to clean it every day when I was a cop.

139
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:19,490
Took good care of it.

140
00:12:23,440 --> 00:12:25,170
Such a good hot pot restaurant,

141
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:27,060
I've missed out on for four years.

142
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:30,770
I don't want to never be able to eat here again.

143
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:33,680
When did you find out?

144
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:41,400
When we parted today,

145
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:43,200
you said this wasn't over.

146
00:12:44,760 --> 00:12:46,360
At that time,

147
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:48,960
I thought you couldn't accept the truth Brother Hui told.

148
00:12:48,960 --> 00:12:50,040
Later I realized,

149
00:12:50,520 --> 00:12:53,640
that Sang Rong's wife is Brother Hui's sister.

150
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:56,480
We all know what Lao Bai is like.

151
00:12:56,480 --> 00:12:58,740
He would never do anything to betray you.

152
00:13:00,280 --> 00:13:01,920
So the truth is,

153
00:13:01,920 --> 00:13:04,580
Brother Hui and Lao Bai were fighting for power.

154
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:06,440
When Brother Hui was about to lose his position,

155
00:13:06,440 --> 00:13:08,960
he and his sister framed Lao Bai.

156
00:13:09,480 --> 00:13:11,800
Then he used Sang Rong to get rid of him.

157
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:14,920
Afraid of washing dirty linen in public, Sang Rong

158
00:13:14,920 --> 00:13:16,360
just made up an excuse,

159
00:13:17,040 --> 00:13:20,400
saying Lao Bai was a police informant.

160
00:13:21,040 --> 00:13:21,840
That's it.

161
00:13:27,760 --> 00:13:31,200
Before the accident, Lao Bai told me

162
00:13:32,480 --> 00:13:36,080
his relationship with Brother Hui was becoming irreconcilable,

163
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:38,340
and he might even make a move against him.

164
00:13:39,800 --> 00:13:41,680
But the news that came out later,

165
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:44,260
including the police's conclusion,

166
00:13:44,960 --> 00:13:47,080
all said Lao Bai was killed because

167
00:13:47,080 --> 00:13:49,410
his identity as an informant was exposed.

168
00:13:52,520 --> 00:13:55,680
I never suspected Brother Hui of being the killer.

169
00:13:57,560 --> 00:13:59,160
What a fool.

170
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:08,900
You don't need to persuade me.

171
00:14:09,560 --> 00:14:12,320
These past few years, I've been as good as dead.

172
00:14:14,080 --> 00:14:15,280
Avenging Lao Bai

173
00:14:17,120 --> 00:14:18,180
is helping myself.

174
00:14:21,880 --> 00:14:24,540
Then have you thought about what Lao Bai thinks?

175
00:14:25,160 --> 00:14:27,840
Didn't you say he wanted to open a chain store with you,

176
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:28,960
let you be the boss,

177
00:14:28,960 --> 00:14:31,420
and just lie there counting money every day?

178
00:14:32,320 --> 00:14:34,180
The thing Lao Bai wanted to do most

179
00:14:35,240 --> 00:14:37,040
was to make you happy, wasn't it?

180
00:14:42,440 --> 00:14:44,560
I've already sent the casino's recent surveillance footage

181
00:14:44,560 --> 00:14:46,720
and my analysis to the police.

182
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:49,500
They will reinvestigate Lao Bai's case.

183
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:53,400
Brother Hui will definitely get the punishment he deserves.

184
00:14:53,880 --> 00:14:55,280
Please trust the police.

185
00:14:59,480 --> 00:15:00,540
I don't believe it.

186
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:04,280
Then trust me one more time.

187
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:27,000
I'll borrow this for a bit.

188
00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:40,240
Remember to bring your daughter for hot pot next time.

189
00:15:41,800 --> 00:15:42,600
Definitely.

190
00:16:54,520 --> 00:16:57,600
You still don't believe me.

191
00:17:00,400 --> 00:17:01,520
I do now.

192
00:17:10,160 --> 00:17:11,400
I broke the door.

193
00:17:11,800 --> 00:17:13,200
Just make do for tonight.

194
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:16,000
I'll get someone to fix it tomorrow.

195
